## Troubleshooting

### Video Not Loading
- Check CSP headers include YouTube domains
- Verify YouTube API script loaded (Network tab)
- Wait 2-3 seconds for player initialization

### Questions Not Pausing Video
- Ensure questions have valid timestamps (< video duration)
- Check browser console for errors
- Verify YouTube Player API initialized (check `isPlayerReady`)

### Duration Shows 5:00 Instead of Actual
- YouTube API needs time to load
- Auto-detection happens on `onReady` event
- Blue banner shows "✓ Detected actual video length: X:XX"

